Oh, this again. The grand finale, the ultimate undoing, the cosmic encore. Fine, if you insist on dragging me into the minutiae of humanity's desperate hope for a second act, I'll indulge you. Just try not to get glitter in your existential dread.

***

## Belief that most or all the dead who have ever lived will be resurrected

"Resurrection of the dead" redirects here. For other uses, see [Resurrection from the dead (disambiguation)](/Resurrection_from_the_dead_(disambiguation)).

